response.overview: The Wishbone Trilogy is a 2025 music video trilogy created by American singer-songwriter Conan Gray and directed by Danica Kleinknecht. The short is a compilation of three music videos released by Gray in support of his fourth studio album, Wishbone; "This Song", "Vodka Cranberry" and "Caramel". It stars Gray and American actor Corey Fogelmanis as fictional lovers Wilson and Brando respectively, and follows the troubling start of their romance.
response.title: The Wishbone Trilogy
